01:07.430 --> 01:08.786
In a shocking turn of events,

01:08.811 --> 01:10.380
Sierra Macy, thought
to have been murdered...

01:10.405 --> 01:12.912
Lazy morning in bed with
your new girlfriend Naomi?

01:12.937 --> 01:15.687
No, we're both a little busy
what with the U.S. Attorney

01:15.712 --> 01:17.578
going through every case
I've ever worked.

01:17.614 --> 01:19.080
You said you were 10 blocks away.

01:19.115 --> 01:20.124
Traffic on Broadway.

01:20.149 --> 01:21.937
You also said
I got to pick my own cases.

01:21.962 --> 01:23.194
Believe me, you'll pick this one.

01:23.219 --> 01:25.085
You see the news this morning
about Sierra Macy?

01:25.121 --> 01:27.488
Woman from Queens,
went missing a decade ago.

01:27.524 --> 01:28.856
Presumed dead until today

01:28.892 --> 01:30.991
when she flagged down
a UPS driver in Yonkers.

01:31.026 --> 01:33.092
- A miracle.
- If it's really her.

01:33.128 --> 01:34.238
Prints are a match. It's her.

01:34.263 --> 01:36.909
I've had my share of lost weekends,
but 10 years? Where's she been?

01:36.934 --> 01:40.299
Apparently held captive by a long-haul
trucker named Peter Gunther.

01:40.335 --> 01:42.368
He died of a heart attack,
Sierra escaped.

01:42.404 --> 01:44.337
You want CIU to review
the conviction of the guy

01:44.372 --> 01:46.272
currently in prison
for her kidnap and murder.

01:46.307 --> 01:48.007
Josh Fleck.
He was a teacher at her school.

01:48.042 --> 01:50.342
He should go free.
Clearly, he didn't kill Sierra.

01:50.377 --> 01:52.110
But Peter Gunther didn't abduct her.

01:52.146 --> 01:54.446
NYPD found his trip sheets in the house.

01:54.481 --> 01:57.516
He was doing a long haul in Iowa
the night she went missing.

01:57.552 --> 01:58.592
Gunther had an accomplice.

01:58.619 --> 02:00.986
Could've been Josh Fleck
or someone else entirely.

02:01.022 --> 02:02.988
How solid is the case against Fleck?

02:03.032 --> 02:04.599
Physical evidence
connects him to the crime,

02:04.624 --> 02:06.490
he lied to the cops, and pled guilty.

02:06.526 --> 02:08.826
Could mean he's guilty,
could mean some bulldog prosecutor

02:08.851 --> 02:11.495
railroaded an innocent guy
into a plea deal.

02:11.531 --> 02:14.398
Is it really her?

02:14.434 --> 02:17.201
- Is Sierra alive?
- Yeah.

02:17.236 --> 02:20.371
Hayes, meet the bulldog
who put Josh Fleck away.

